0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-2-scaled.jpg 1537w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-2-728x1042.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-2-768x1099.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-2-1073x1536.jpg 1073w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-2-1431x2048.jpg 1431w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-2-150x215.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-2-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSo that’s where my chicken and stuffing bake comes in. It’s easy. It doesn’t take forever to prepare or roast. And it makes a manageable amount of food with just a little bit of extra stuffing. Because \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2020/11/best-stuffing-recipe/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003estuffing\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e is what makes the Thanksgiving meal. I wait all year for it. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-3-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"thanksgiving chicken and stuffing\" width=\"1631\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Thanksgiving Chicken and Stuffing Bake with Easy Gravy.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-3-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/thanksgiving-chicken-and-stuffing-3-sca